	<item>
		<title>Press: &#8216;Pacific Soul&#8217; by Jaume Plensa at Pacific Gate by Bosa</title>
		<link>https://sprec.com/news/2017/02/press-jaume-plensa-selects-downtown-san-diegos-pacific-gate-by-bosa-high-rise-for-his-next-west-coast-public-installation/</link>
